        </p>
        <p>
          On the fan side, the value proposition is equally compelling. Supporters acquire actual ownership in their favorite sports properties, creating both emotional and financial investment in team performance. This ownership isn't static either—the NFT model enables secondary market trading, where fans can strategically buy and sell zones based on team performance trends and upcoming matchups.
        </p>
